data.title: Carlos Delfino news and rumors
data.text:
NBA news and rumors about Carlos Delfino

News publishing in english has been temporarely discontinued. You can access here to our news archive. For the latest NBA news, you can visit our NBA news site in spanish.

NBA rumors

Clippers plan to waive Carlos Delfino, Miroslav Raduljica

According to a person with knowledge of the Clippers' situation, it's likely that Carlos Delfino will be waived using what's deemed the "stretch provision."

NBA market

Clippers acquire Delfino, Raduljica from Bucks for Jared Dudley

The Clippers has acquired Carlos Delfino, Miroslav Raduljica and a 2015 second round draft pick from the Bucks in exchange for Jared Dudley.
